    "(c) Comparing human engineering faculty with AI models across different domains reveals that, in certain areas, faculty members specializing in specific domains outperform AI models.",
    "As indicated in (a), providing an explanation before the answer yields slightly better results, a trend more evident in this context.",
    "(d) Analysis of varying prompts and their respective accuracies.",
    "Figure 4:4Figure 4: Comparison of answers between random guessing and responses from undergraduate students in non-mechanical engineering (non-ME) majors.",
